== vim ~/.ssh/config

Host github-as-indera
    HostName github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile /Users/asura/.ssh/id_rsa
    IdentitiesOnly yes

== clone and change the remote url

git clone https://github.com/indera/indera.github.io
git remote set-url origin git@github-as-indera:indera/indera.github.io.git


== push without entering a password 

magic :)
